events.name: Alabama Crimson Tide at Mississippi State Bulldogs

headlines.description: T.J. Yeldon rushed for 160 yards, A.J. McCarron threw two touchdown passes and No. 1 Alabama overcame four turnovers to beat Mississippi State 20-7 on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bama slogs way by Miss. St.

events.name: Syracuse Orange at Florida State Seminoles

headlines.description: Jameis Winston showed no effects from a tumultuous week during No. 2 Florida State's 59-3 win against Syracuse on Saturday. The redshirt quarterback completed 19-of-21 passes for 277 yards and two touchdowns as the Seminoles rolled.
headlines.shortLinkText: Winston, Florida State drub Syracuse

events.name: Ohio State Buckeyes at Illinois Fighting Illini

headlines.description: Carlos Hyde ran for 246 yards and four touchdowns and Braxton Miller had another 184 yards rushing and two scores Saturday to push No. 3 Ohio State past Illinois 60-35.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ohio State holds off Illinois

events.name: Stanford Cardinal at USC Trojans

headlines.description: Andre Heidari kicked a 47-yard field goal with 19 seconds to play, and Southern California's stalwart defense repeatedly came up big in a 20-17 victory over No. 4 Stanford on Saturday night.

events.name: Oregon State Beavers at Arizona State Sun Devils
